summary: Chapter 8, Roose part IV Fickle Games (Mock(ing)bird part II): A redemption fic in which Petyr finds himself punished by the...
caption:
Chapter 8, Roose part IV

Fickle Games (Mock(ing)bird part II): A redemption fic in which Petyr finds himself punished by the Gods and was sent to purgatory to suffer without his wits and memory of his past self for centuries. He is left at the mercy of Ramsay Bolton as an inmate in an insane asylum. Meanwhile, Sansa Stark has a new life in our plane of existence, but is determined to save Petyr’s condemned soul from purgatory.

This post: Petyr throws a feast at lord Bolton’s expense and Sansa has some nice family get-to-gether time…Start reading from the beginning, or follow me here

title: [Spoilers] Arya's list and Ilyn Payne
body:
So the show kept us reminding us that Ilyn Payne was part of Arya’s list in the first few seasons but he magically disappeared from the list in the last seasons.

I’m aware that the actor who played Ilyn had some kind of cancer but I think I read somewhere that he recovered. Do you guys think we will see Ilyn Payne ever again? Will Arya kill him?

Imo this will feel like such a wasted dropped story line if they don’t address him ever again. He was the one who killed Ned after all. Thoughts?



Source: https://ift.tt/2OnbKeb
